<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Gannett Co. Names
   Watson to Head
   Newspaper Group
   ----
   By Patrick M. Reilly
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/31/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
